E2.5MOM for 15min:
2 Cleans
*at the first rep of each set pause for 3sec under the knee and 3sec at the catch (squat)

6 Alternating arms DB Thrusters (#22.5/15, x2)
9 Pushups

*for the thrusters hold 2 dbs on the shoulders and alternate reps between arms

Endurance:

Row 500m
40 Walking Lunges
30 Pushups
20 SDHP (#20/15)
10 Bar facing burpees
